event.title: COVID-19 and what we are doing
event.description:
To The Amazing Sydney Community

We believe it is time to communicate directly with you. No fancy graphics, no GIFs, no filtered food images.

Obviously, the COVID-19 situation is here for a while and we are treating this situation as seriously as you are.

This is our commitment to you

• We understand that our community needs to eat so we intend to remain open until the Australian Government says otherwise

• We intend to never stop offering a takeaway service (by phone or online) and a home delivery service via MENULOG to 50  suburbs across Sydney

• If you need special assistance, please contact us and we will do our utmost to help

We have been proactive with respect to isolation and hygiene to help protect the broader Sydney community. Two weeks prior to the Australian Government announcing the 14-day isolation policy, we instructed all staff that all non-essential overseas travel was banned. All returning staff from overseas were ordered to self-isolate.
